---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import '../styles/resources.css';
---
<Site
  title="Tools — Navon"
  description="Interactive tools from Navon — model sovereign compute costs, plan deployments, and more. Starting with the pricing calculator, with more tools shipping over time."
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>Tools</div>
      <h1 class="page-title reveal">Put the numbers<br/><span class="accent">in your own hands.</span></h1>
      <p class="page-lede reveal d1" style="margin-top:24px;">
        Interactive, self-serve tools to model, plan, and evaluate sovereign
        compute on your terms — no sales call required. We start with the
        pricing calculator and add more over time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <svg class="hero-glyph tech draw" viewBox="0 0 460 380" aria-hidden="true">
      <g class="hair">
        <rect x="40" y="40" width="160" height="120" fill="none"/>
        <rect x="240" y="40" width="180" height="120" fill="none"/>
        <rect x="40" y="200" width="160" height="120" fill="none"/>
        <rect x="240" y="200" width="180" height="120" fill="none"/>
      </g>
      <rect x="40" y="40" width="160" height="120" class="signal" opacity="0.12"/>
      <text x="52" y="58" font-size="9" letter-spacing="2" class="label-signal">CALCULATOR</text>
      <text x="252" y="58" font-size="9" letter-spacing="2" fill="#9E9F9B">SOON</text>
      <text x="52" y="218" font-size="9" letter-spacing="2" fill="#9E9F9B">SOON</text>
      <text x="252" y="218" font-size="9" letter-spacing="2" fill="#9E9F9B">SOON</text>
      <text x="60" y="370" font-size="10" letter-spacing="2" fill="#9E9F9B" font-family="JetBrains Mono">ONE WORKBENCH · MANY TOOLS</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Tools grid -->
<section class="resources-grid">

  <a class="res-card res-card--tool reveal" href="calculator.html">
    <div class="glyph">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="tech" aria-hidden="true">
        <g class="hair">
          <line x1="40" y1="40" x2="40" y2="160"/>
          <line x1="280" y1="40" x2="280" y2="160"/>
        </g>
        <rect x="40" y="40" width="80" height="120" class="signal" opacity="0.1"/>
        <rect x="130" y="40" width="80" height="120" class="signal" opacity="0.06"/>
        <rect x="220" y="40" width="60" height="120" class="signal" opacity="0.03"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="130" x2="120" y2="130" class="signal" stroke-width="1.4"/>
        <line x1="130" y1="148" x2="210" y2="148" class="signal" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.6"/>
        <line x1="220" y1="155" x2="280" y2="155" class="signal" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.35"/>
        <text x="46" y="56" font-size="8" letter-spacing="1.5" class="label-signal">COST</text>
        <text x="136" y="56" font-size="8" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="#9E9F9B">EU</text>
        <text x="226" y="56" font-size="8" letter-spacing="1.5" fill="#9E9F9B">MKT</text>
        <text x="55" y="170" font-size="10" letter-spacing="2" fill="#E7FF00" font-family="JetBrains Mono">$0.41 / 1M TOKENS</text>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="num">01 / PRICING TOOL <span class="badge badge--tool">Calculator</span></div>
    <h3>Model your sovereign compute costs.</h3>
    <p>Load the Navon Hells Gate reference model, substitute your market inputs, and share a scenario with your CFO — no sales call required.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span>Interactive · client-side</span><span class="arrow">→</span></div>
  </a>

  <a class="res-card coming reveal d1" href="#" onclick="event.preventDefault(); alert('More tools coming soon.');">
    <div class="glyph">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="tech" aria-hidden="true">
        <g class="hair">
          <rect x="60" y="40" width="200" height="100" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="60" y1="70" x2="260" y2="70"/>
          <line x1="110" y1="40" x2="110" y2="140"/>
        </g>
        <rect x="60" y="40" width="50" height="30" class="signal" opacity="0.5"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="num">02 / DEPLOYMENT PLANNER <span class="badge">Soon</span></div>
    <h3>Size a pod to your load.</h3>
    <p>Map your workload to modular pod count, power draw, and footprint — a fast first pass before an engineering scoping call.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span>Coming soon</span><span class="arrow">→</span></div>
  </a>

  <a class="res-card coming reveal d2" href="#" onclick="event.preventDefault(); alert('More tools coming soon.');">
    <div class="glyph">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="tech" aria-hidden="true">
        <g class="hair">
          <circle cx="160" cy="90" r="50" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="160" y1="40" x2="160" y2="90"/>
          <line x1="160" y1="90" x2="200" y2="110"/>
        </g>
        <path d="M160 90 L160 40 A50 50 0 0 1 205 75 Z" class="signal" opacity="0.18"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="num">03 / CARBON ESTIMATOR <span class="badge">Soon</span></div>
    <h3>Compare emissions vs hyperscalers.</h3>
    <p>Estimate the carbon footprint of a workload on geothermal-backed Navon compute against equivalent public-cloud regions.</p>
    <div class="meta"><span>Coming soon</span><span class="arrow">→</span></div>
  </a>

</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="signup">
  <div class="signup-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="mark"></span>Need something specific?</div>
      <h2 class="reveal">Tell us what you'd<br/>want to <span class="accent">model.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal d1">
      <p style="color:var(--light); font-size:16px; line-height:1.55; max-width:46ch; margin:0 0 24px;">
        We're building these tools around the questions buyers and engineers actually ask. If there's a calculation you wish you could self-serve, tell us.
      </p>
      <div class="dual-cta">
        <a href="about.html#contact" class="cta">Suggest a tool <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="calculator.html" class="cta-ghost">Open the calculator <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Site>
